Class DataRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.zankowski.yahoofinanceapi.DataRequest

  • public class DataRequest
extends java.lang.Object

    Date: 19.09.2015

    This class has been made to hold DataType and delay (in milliseconds) value for it needed to requests in Session calls. Example values holded in object:

    DataType: DataType.LAST_TRADE_PRICE    Delay: 1000

    Author:
    Wojciech Zankowski
